Invocation Name: cavehill facts
des:
UWI Cavehill is a University in the Caribbean Island of Barbados. To learn more information about the culture of the university ask for UWI Cavehill Facts.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch cavehill facts" or "Alexa, open cavehill facts" to get a fact.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
